# Draygon 2 Logic

## Mode 1

Initial boss mode.
Walking left/right across top of screen, maybe throwing balls.

* Every 32 frames (by $4e0), if random number is odd and global counter positive,
    * If (x^y) is *even* then jump straight to initiating lasers
    * This can be achieved by going to bottom row, then all the way right


## Mode 2

Walking down to bottom of screen to shoot nuper.







## Random numbers

Read value $0e index into 64-byte table at $357e4 => 0..7

## Properties

$4e0: timer - reassess action every 32 frames
$600: current mode
$620: timer
$6e0: increments to 0..9
